            "id": 6010086,
            "title": "〈台股盤後〉台積電、AI股稍息 小跌13點收21660點 周線翻紅漲313點",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>台股今 (6) 日在台積電、AI 股熄火，以及迎來周末下，呈現量縮震盪，終場小跌 13.77 點收 21660.66 點，成交金額 2942 億元；不過，<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>本周上漲 313 點，周線終止連二黑。</p></section><p></p><div class=\"c1hvmcli\"><figure><div class=\"iirgi4a\"><img alt=\"cover image of news article\" class=\"cr8g41v\" data-nimg=\"fill\" decoding=\"async\" fetchpriority=\"high\" sizes=\"\n            (max-width: 1024px) 100% 406px,\n            (max-width: 768px) 100% 193px\n          \" src=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010086%2Fl%2F02cb56bc6f7fcc49431d16e9f087b006.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\" srcset=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010086%2Fl%2F02cb56bc6f7fcc49431d16e9f087b006.jpg&amp;w=16&amp;q=75 16w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010086%2Fl%2F02cb56bc6f7fcc49431d16e9f087b006.jpg&amp;w=32&amp;q=75 32w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010086%2Fl%2F02cb56bc6f7fcc49431d16e9f087b006.jpg&amp;w=48&amp;q=75 48w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010086%2Fl%2F02cb56bc6f7fcc49431d16e9f087b006.jpg&amp;w=64&amp;q=75 64w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010086%2Fl%2F02cb56bc6f7fcc49431d16e9f087b006.jpg&amp;w=96&amp;q=75 96w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010086%2Fl%2F02cb56bc6f7fcc49431d16e9f087b006.jpg&amp;w=128&amp;q=75 128w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010086%2Fl%2F02cb56bc6f7fcc49431d16e9f087b006.jpg&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 256w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010086%2Fl%2F02cb56bc6f7fcc49431d16e9f087b006.jpg&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010086%2Fl%2F02cb56bc6f7fcc49431d16e9f087b006.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010086%2Fl%2F02cb56bc6f7fcc49431d16e9f087b006.jpg&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010086%2Fl%2F02cb56bc6f7fcc49431d16e9f087b006.jpg&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010086%2Fl%2F02cb56bc6f7fcc49431d16e9f087b006.jpg&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010086%2Fl%2F02cb56bc6f7fcc49431d16e9f087b006.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010086%2Fl%2F02cb56bc6f7fcc49431d16e9f087b006.jpg&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010086%2Fl%2F02cb56bc6f7fcc49431d16e9f087b006.jpg&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010086%2Fl%2F02cb56bc6f7fcc49431d16e9f087b006.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\"/></div><figcaption class=\"c1gcnfq1\">〈台股盤後〉台積電、AI股稍息 小跌13點收21660點 周線翻紅漲313點。(鉅亨網資料照)</figcaption></figure></div><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>台積電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2330:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2330\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2330-TW</a>) 近千元大關情怯，今日收盤下跌 3 元來到 995 元；AI 股同步回檔，鴻海 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2317:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2317\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2317-TW</a>)5 月營收雖然創同期新高，但今日仍下跌 1.6%，廣達 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2382:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2382\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2382-TW</a>) 也收黑，緯創 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3231:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3231\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3231-TW</a>)、貿聯 - KY(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3665:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3665\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3665-TW</a>) 更是大跌逾 4%。</p></section><section>\n</section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>高價股方面，創意 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3443:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3443\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3443-TW</a>) 跌 3.8%、川湖 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2059:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2059\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2059-TW</a>) 也跌近 3%，不過，旭隼 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6409:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6409\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6409-TW</a>) 大漲逾 6%。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>而傳產族群相較電子股，表現較佳，美國總統川普與中國國家主席習近平通話，激勵國際油價上漲，台塑四寶今日連袂上攻，台化 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1326:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1326\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1326-TW</a>) 漲 3.6%、台塑化 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6505:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6505\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6505-TW</a>) 及台塑 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1301:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1301\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1301-TW</a>) 也漲近 3%，南亞 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1303:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1303\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1303-TW</a>) 也收紅。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section></main>",
